node.title: Motorcyclist dies in Marlborough
node.description: A motorcyclist has died in a crash in Renwick this morning.
node.content:
["A motorcyclist has died in a crash in Marlborough this morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Tim Brown\n
", "The crash, on an unnamed road near the intersection of State Highway 6 and State Highway 62 at Renwick, was reported to Police at 10.40am.", "No other vehicles were involved.", "Police enquiries into the circumstances of the crash are under way."]
